    "section_url": "https://fastapi.tiangolo.com/tutorial/server-sent-events/#resuming-with-last-event-id",
    "section_text": "When a browser reconnects after a connection drop, it sends the last received id in the Last-Event-ID header.\n\nYou can read it as a header parameter and use it to resume the stream from where the client left off:",
